;Supporting the <a href="%(coral)s">Coral Project</a>, which works to improve how journalists and communities engage on news websites, including tools like <a href="%(talk)s">Talk</a>, that aims to create smarter, safer comments sections.
Tajin niqato' ri <a href="%(coral)s">Coral Nuk'samaj</a>, ri nisamäj richin nub'än rutzil rub'eyal chi ri taq tzijonela' chuqa' taq tinamït tikinima' ki' pa ri taq ruxaq rajk'amaya'l tzijob'äl, achi'el chuqa' taq samajib'äl <a href="%(talk)s">Talk</a>ri rojqan yerunük' na'owinäq chuqa' jikonem taq kik'ojlib'al tzijol.


